// Header
a(name='write')
.intro-header
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12
        .intro-message
          h1 Storyline Nai
          h3 Writing Nairobi, a story at a time.
          hr.intro-divider
          ul.list-inline.intro-social-buttons
            li
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='https://twitter.com/SBootstrap')
                i.fa.fa-arrow-right.fa-fw
                span.network-name Sign Up
            li
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='https://github.com/IronSummitMedia/startbootstrap')
                i.fa.fa-sign-in.fa-fw
                span.network-name Sign In
  // /.container
// /.intro-header
// Page Content
a(name='share')
.content-section-a
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading Write your Story
        p.lead
          | We have a user friendly portal that allows you to write your story. Anything that interests you counts, anything that happened within Nairobi counts. The share your story with the world.
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-2.col-sm-6
        img.img-responsive(src='img/ipad.png' alt='')
  // /.container
// /.content-section-a
.content-section-b
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-lg-offset-1.col-sm-push-6.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer
        .clearfix
        h2.section-heading Share your Story
        p.lead
          | With Storyline you will be able to share your stories with a huge audience keen on stories out of Nairobi. So type away to share your story with others.
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-pull-6.col-sm-6
        img.img-responsive(src='img/dog.png' alt='')
  // /.container
// /.content-section-b
.content-section-a
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-5.col-sm-6
        hr.section-heading-spacer
        .clearfix
